public class ScreenHandler
extends javafx.application.Application
implements LoginScreenController.LoginScreenControllerListener, AccountCreationController.AccountCreationControllerListener, MainPageController.MainPageControllerListener, AccountModificationController.AccountModificationControllerListener, ProjectSelectionController.ProjectSelectionControllerListener
Main controller class used to decide which screen to show depending on the notifications received from lower tier controllers using interfaces
